Package: EnvExpInd
Type: Package
Title: Environmental Exposure on the Individual Level
Imports: gstat,RCurl,dplyr,stringi,sp,maptools
Version: 0.1.0
Depends: R(>= 3.5.0)
Authors@R: person("Bing","Zhang", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "zhangb269@mail2.sysu.edu.cn")
Description: Tools for the assessment of the environmental exposure. The package provides three methods (nearest monitoring site, inverse distance weighted, ordinary kriging) to calculate the environmental exposure (air pollution or temperature) on the individual level.
URL: https://github.com/Spatial-R/EnvExpInd
